          %a(href='https://maps.google.com/maps?q=35.716152,139.764419&hl=ja&num=1&t=m&z=16' target='_blank') 2-11-16 Yayoi, Bunkyo-ku, Tokyo
          %br/
          Phone: +81 (3) 5841 6754

        %p#copyright Copyright &copy; 2008-2013 Database Center for Life Science (DBCLS)

    = yield :javascript
